1. *Moj* mama je veoma ljubazna. (My mom is very kind.)
2. *Mom* čoveku je bilo veoma teško da se izbori sa svim problemima. (The man had a hard time dealing with all the problems.)
3. *Momci* su se igrali na livadi. (The boys were playing in the meadow.)
4. *Mamu* sam zamolio da mi pomogne. (I asked mom to help me.)